          well here i am, fucked up, listening to the new linkin park cd. very cool, but i'm worried, i'm worried that lexa is ignoring me, because i haven't been able to get in touch with her for several days. i'm afraid that she's decided she doesn't actually like me, but i don't really have any evidence for that conclusion. for a few days, i felt like things were finally going -right- in my life. now i have to wonder if that was just an illussion. at the very least i stiull have my work, which i am doing well. assistant manager, with talk of me ending up as a store manager when i'm ready for it. lots of responsibility, but i like that. i think i'm up for it.<br /><br />my sister has a friend over for a few weeks. her name is Eva, and she's from germany. it's kinda weird, it's like my family sorta gained another member. which reminds me, hehe. fuck it. my sister makes more money than me per hour, and she's had a job for about a week. that's a pretty sweet job.<br /><br />so fucked up. so fucked up.<br /><br />chill wit' ya laters all. peace --<br />
